race.comment: SIVO BANNER (1) is a well performed dog and winner of 24 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at this track (16.89). Form here at this distance is sound. Boasts a strong record from this draw with three wins and two minor placings from six starts. Has ability and is a key runner. DRINK MICKEYS (8) turned in a fair 5th placed finish last time at Capalaba over 366m (20.48). Has ability and can measure up. SWING BY (7) drifted back from wide but charged home to hit the frame when 4 lengths from the winner (19.32) at this track in Grade 5. Winning chance. HEAD WEST (2) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can atone.
